name: Leda y el Cisne
description: Photography taken with a nikon d5200 camera on 06/29/18 at 12:07pm in Mineral del Monte, Hidalgo which is a very very small town known for its mining history and good food. On its "main plaza" it has a kiosko and a fountain which on the top has a sculpture of "Leda and the Swan" from greek mythology, seen here accompanied for a moment by a pigeon who didn't took long to fly away.
